<plot>When Bradley Henderson, a mild mannered accountant, wakes up to a gun in his face, his captor tells him that he has five minutes to prepare for a fight to the death. The process is random. Even to his captor, the purpose of the fight is unknown. In Alternative Dispute Resolution, a world of seemingly unknown events unfold into a not so random process of settling differences.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?032983</url></doc>
